'''''King Solomon's Mines''''' ni film yasohotse muri 1985 , iturutse kuri novel yitwa King Solomon's Mines yanditswe na  H. Rider yajonjogoye<ref>https://www.amazon.com/Solomons-Mines-Region-Richard-Chamberlain/dp/B01GUP5KDU</ref> . Irimo Richard Chamberlain, Sharon Stone, Herbert Lom na John Rhys-Davies<ref>https://www.nathanrabin.com/happy-place/2017/6/5/stuff-i-got-for-free-king-solomons-mines-1986</ref> . Yahinduwe na Gene Quintano na James R. Silke kandi iyobowe na J. Lee Thompson<ref>https://www.filmaffinity.com/us/film639216.html</ref> . Iyi verisiyo yinkuru yari yoroheje,  urwenya, iganisha ku  gusebya ''Indiana Jones'' (aho umukinnyi wa francise Rhys-Davies yagaragaye mubice bibiri). Yafatiwe amashusho hanze ya [[Harare]] muri [[Zimbabwe]] . <ref>https://in.bookmyshow.com/chennai/movies/king-solomons-mines/ET00008706</ref>

Yakurikiwe nuruhererekane ''[[:en:Allan_Quatermain_and_the_Lost_City_of_Gold|Allan Quatermain and the Lost City of Gold]]'' (1986) kandi yagombaga gukurikirwa nuruhererekane rutigeze rukorwa<ref>http://basementrejects.com/review/king-solomons-mines-1985/</ref>, igerageza ry'ambere ryaba rishingiye kuri ''She na Allan'', ikindi gitabo cya Haggard<ref>https://allanquartermaine.fandom.com/wiki/King_Solomon%27s_Mines</ref>, hanyuma kugerageza bwa kabiri kwitwa ''Allan Quatermain na Jewel of the East'' kandi iyobowe na producer Golan.<ref>https://en-academic.com/dic.nsf/enwiki/5893047</ref><ref>https://www.themoviedb.org/movie/9838-king-solomon-s-mines</ref>

